OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry through
OL,6,Fthe evening and overnight. Clear skies
OL,7,Fseeing the development of some low
OL,8,Fcloud, and the chance of mist and fog
OL,9,Fthrough the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAny early low cloud, mist
OL,12,Fand fog clearing to leave a dry,
OL,13,Fbright and mild afternoon. Cloud
OL,14,Fthickening into the evening however.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBecoming
OL,17,Fcloudier with some light rain into
OL,18,FFriday, and conditions remaining
OL,19,Fgenerally cloudy and mild into the
OL,20,Fweekend, with further light rain at
OL,21,Ftimes.
